{"tid":1759133,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 馬鞍山某中學發現爆炸品","createTime":"2019-11-27T12:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T14:56:10.000Z","uid":225821,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"689396b3451931ce7446396b3a8da9c07e7bba77","tid":1759133,"uid":225821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:53:53.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山錦英路<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">明愛馬鞍山中學</span></span>，今日(27日)下午2時許，職員發現校園內有懷疑炸藥，於是通知消防處，兩輛消防車及一輛救護車趕至學校戒備。其後，警方接獲通知到場，並通知爆炸品處理課人員到場處理，檢查該些炸藥。<br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查後，以涉嫌管有炸藥拘捕兩名分別姓趙(17歲)及姓黎(18歲)男子，帶署扣查，案件由新界南總區重案組接手。據了解，兩名被捕男子為該校中五及中六學生，該校明日（28日）會停課。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8419bc07d6a3e240413eecfd24acb9a4f6b16138","tid":1759133,"uid":225821,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NtqwtNL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtqwtNL.jpg&h=5ae7a085&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ntFXpk5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FntFXpk5.gif&h=f91610a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4586dd6ba78859878446365bc3b5610cf6c6027","tid":1759133,"uid":132587,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:55:47.000Z","msg":"拉左既話個級無人上堂架啦wor"},{"pid":"92442fdb1afeafbe6fbb8a7fb9dbf8d1d9637834","tid":1759133,"uid":225821,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"d4586dd6ba78859878446365bc3b5610cf6c6027","tid":1759133,"uid":132587,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:55:47.000Z","m